msgstr ":envvar:`mail/dovecot/process/mail_fsync`\\ ``=always``"

#: ../../mail/configuration-server.rst:292
msgid ""
"To achieve higher performance, index files can be kept on the local "
"servers disk, instead of storing them together with the messages on NFS. "
