#: ../../mail/configuration-server.rst:324
msgid ""
"In a default |UCSUCS| configuration Dovecot allows ``400`` concurrent "
"IMAP and POP3 connections each. That is enough to serve at least 100 "
"concurrently logged in IMAP users, possibly a lot more."
